query:
UPDATE island_guides ig
JOIN atolls a ON LOWER(REPLACE(ig.atoll, ' ', '')) = LOWER(REPLACE(a.name, ' ', ''))
SET ig.atollId = a.id
WHERE ig.atollId IS NULL
